quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,91,Avo vakapatsanura Qur’aan muzvidimbu zvidumbu (vakatenda muzvimwe uye vakaramba zvimwe)
  15,92,"Saka ndinopika naTenzi vako (Muhammad (SAW)), zvirokwazvo, tichava tinovabvunza vese"
  15,93,Maererano neizvo zvavaiita
  15,94,"Naizvozvo paridza pachena zvawakakomekedzwa (Islaam), ova unosiyana neavo vasingatendi"
  15,95,Zvirokwazvo! Tichava tinokukwanira kune avo vanokushoropodza
  15,96,Avo vanosanganisa Allah neumwe mwari; asi vachasvika pakuziva
  15,97,"Zvirokwazvo, tinoziva kuti zvavanotaura zvinokubata-bata muhana mako"
  15,98,Naizvozvo rumbidza kurumbidzwa kwaTenzi vako uye ova pakati peavo vanopfugama
  15,99,Uye namata Tenzi vako kusvikira rufu rwauya kwauri
  16,1,"Murawo wakatarwa naAllah (Zuva Rekutongwa) uchasvika, saka musave munoda kuukurumidzisa. Kurumbidzwa ngakuve kwavari uye vari pamusoro pezvese zvavanovasanganisa nazvo"
  16,2,"Vanotumidzira ngirozi neRooh (Mashoko avo) nemurawo wavo kune wavada kubva kune varanda vavo (vachiti): “Yambirai (vanhu) kuti Laa ilaaha illaa Ana (Hapana anekodzero yekunamatwa kunze kwangu), saka ityai inini (nekusaita mabasa akaipa).”"
  16,3,Vakasika matenga nenyika muchokwadi. Vari pamusoro pezvese zvavanovasanganisa nazvo
  16,4,"Vakasika munhu kubva kuNutfah (musanganiswa wemvura yababa naamai), asi tarisai, anobva aita mupikisi ari pachena"
  16,5,"Uye nemombe, vakakusikirai; munowana kubva madziri kudziirwa (mbasha dzinodziya) nezvakati wandei zvinobatsira, uye kubva madziri munodya"
  16,6,"Uye munowana kubva madziri runako pamunodzitora kubva kumafuro manheru, uye nepamunodziendesa kumafuro mangwanani"